  "html": "\n<div><center>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td><font><img src=\"../images/R.gif\"/> </font><b>One-eyed\n        merchant</b><hr noshade=\"\"/>\n<p>I.e., Mr. Eugenides, \"one-eyed\" because the\n        figure is in profile on the card and also a suggestion of\n        evil or crookedness, or a pirate. (NA) </p>\n<p><font><em>reference topics</em></font></p>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td>link two</td>\n<td><a href=\"title_A.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"Waste_A.htm\"><font>back to \"The Waste Land\" </font></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank_A.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</center></div>\n",
  "text": "One-eyed merchant I.e., Mr. Eugenides, \"one-eyed\" because the figure is in profile on the card and also a suggestion of evil or crookedness, or a pirate. (NA) reference topics link two back to \"The Waste Land\"",
